exceptions.exn: In environment i, j, n, m : nat H : swap n = swap m The term "n" has type "nat" while it is expected to have type "?n <> i".
In environment i, j, n, m : nat H : swap n = swap m The term "m" has type "nat" while it is expected to have type "?n <> i".

original: intros H. pose proof (swap_spec n) as H0. pose proof (swap_spec m) as H1. specialize (H0 ltac:(auto) ltac:(auto)). specialize (H1 ltac:(auto) ltac:(auto)). intros H2. pose proof (swap_involutive n) as H3. pose proof (swap_involutive m) as H4. rewrite H in H2. rewrite H3 in H2. rewrite H4 in H2. auto.
